<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bilan de phosphore</title>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/7.8.5/d3.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    #graph {
      flex: 1;
    }
    #controls {
      width: 300px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      overflow-y: auto;
      height: 100vh;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .node-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-anchor: middle;
      pointer-events: none;
      fill: #333;
    }
    .tooltip {
      position: absolute;
      padding: 10px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      pointer-events: none;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    #input-controls div {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
    }
    #input-controls div.selected {
      border-color: #1e90ff;
      background: #f0f8ff;
    }
    #input-controls input {
      width: 60px;
      margin: 5px;
      padding: 3px;
    }
    #input-controls label {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 40px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    #thickness-basis {
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 5px;
    }
    h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 1em;
      margin-left: 1em;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18pt;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 0em;
      padding-bottom: 0em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="graph">
    
    <h1>Treated effluent Phosphorus is X mg/L, raising the concentration in the Lake form X to Y mg/L</h1>
    <h1>What is the impact of urine and fecal diversion on the environment?</h1>

  </div>
  <div id="controls">
    <h3>Controls:</h3>
    <label for="thickness-basis">Arrow Thickness Based On:</label>
    <select id="thickness-basis">
      <option value="Q*P">Phosphorus, g P/d</option>
      <option value="Q*COD">Organic Matter, g COD/d</option>
      <option value="Q*N">Nitrogen, g N/d</option>
      <option value="Q">Volume, L/d</option>
    </select>
    <div id="input-params"></div>
    <div id="input-controls"></div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/input-json.js"> </script>
  <script src="/js/script.js"> </script>
</body>
</html>